{"tid":1790752,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[回帶2015採訪]20歲的南野拓實：目標是英超，想追隨高普的腳步去利物浦。","createTime":"2019-12-20T08:37:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-20T12:29:37.000Z","uid":103207,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7961fcd062032f79408eaef22dd9d685a4bc2217","tid":1790752,"uid":103207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T08:37:56.000Z","msg":"昨天利物浦官方宣佈日本前鋒南野拓實正式加盟。日本朝日電視台回顧了2015年12月南野拓實接受採訪時的視頻畫面。<br />\n<br />\n採訪<span style=\"color: red;\">取材於薩爾茨堡，當時年僅20歲的南野拓實被問及未來想去哪裡發展時，羞澀但充滿期待地表示自己的目標是英超，想追隨克洛普的腳步去利物浦。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n四年之後，南野拓實完成了美好的年輕夢想，主持人清水俊輔對這段勵志的經歷贊嘆不已。在接受利物浦官網採訪時，南野拓實說道：「加盟利物浦是我一直以來的願望，我夢想著成為利物浦的一員，很高興我能將夢想變成了現實。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Xoyf1RuOZeA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DXoyf1RuOZeA&d=1CRlZafk7JeE%2BAtxbqKu5fMFbVPULjdiAdi6tpyrPMY%3D&h=b493bed2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Xoyf1RuOZeA</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05e60c668733ee1c77deb8f1a2e1f4d4e539d404","tid":1790752,"uid":5649,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T08:41:33.000Z","msg":"4年前已經鋪路陷害香港，死蘿蔔頭子"},{"pid":"1b03f0918c9a20461822b0ad161eb7b9f28c4796","tid":1790752,"uid":180462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"05e60c668733ee1c77deb8f1a2e1f4d4e539d404","tid":1790752,"uid":5649,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T08:41:33.000Z","msg":"4年前已經鋪路陷害香港，死蘿蔔頭子"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T09:18:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AVoM683.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAVoM683.jpg&h=9c3b2949&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e1d2fca129c4f2022d8e9d3fc99ea3de4e6d70e9","tid":1790752,"uid":84081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-20T12:29:37.000Z","msg":"細個鐘意車路士既冇個去到車<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n包皮<br />\n辛祖<br />\nPepe"}]}